dimorph 0.1.2
  • Reference

    Finite Mixture Analysis table from Godfrey et al. (1993)

    FMAtable.Rd

    Values of k for a given sample size for the calculation of distribution means for a Gaussian finite mixture using equations in Godfrey et al. (1993). k gives the mean expected number of standard deviations (as measured for the whole dataset) represented in the observed data range for a given sample size.

    data(FMAtable)

    Format

    An object of class data.frame with 99 rows and 2 columns.

    References

    Godfrey LR, Lyon SK, Sutherland MR. (1993) Sexual dimorphism in large-bodied primates: The case of the subfossil lemurs. American Journal of Physical Anthropology. 90:315-334. (https://doi.org/10.1002/ajpa.1330900306)

    Examples
